Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Do you want\Nsome rolled omelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:04.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:05.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very\Nmuch for offering,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I am so sick and tired of that\Nsmug little teacher's pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:11.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We haven't met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of Hayama's?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2A]\NOkay, everyone. It's lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,See you all back here\Nafter the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:55.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2B]\NSo what'd you bring for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2C]\NI'm buying today, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2D]\NLet's hurry. I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NMy name is Yoko Nishikawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:06.04,Main,,0,0,0,,and I come from\Na wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:09.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, my father's\Ncompany fell on hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,It went bankrupt, and now I have\Nto live like an ordinary girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:15.30,Main,,0,0,0,,But it might not be\Nas bad as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:18.05,Main,,0,0,0,,The other day, something\Nwonderful happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:20.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I made two new friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Hey. Do you want\Nsome rolled omelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NOh... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:29.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very\Nmuch for offering,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on. Just have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But if I do that, there\Nwill be less left for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] No, it's your lunch.\NI really can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NSure you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NNo, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,--[FUTABA] That's enough!\N--[HAYAMA] Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThis is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You're being so polite you'd\Nthink you'd never met before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:48.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't we all just relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure. What'd you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:52.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,For starters, we could come up\Nwith nicknames for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:56.68,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the kinda\Nthing friends do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.\NWe are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Are we really\Ngood enough friends
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.14,Main,,0,0,0,,for nicknames, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThat's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:10.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Nah, maybe not.\NIt's way too early
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Yoko,\Nwe're just teasing. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[rustling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[CAT meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[CAT meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:33.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose it must be a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA squealing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:36.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:37.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[CAT meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NCan't breathe! It's too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] What's the matter,\Nwiddle kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Is poor widdle kitty wost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've ever seen\Nher enjoy herself like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:56.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Freaky, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:57.82,Main,,0,0,0,,She's kinda got\Na thing for cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, I love cats,\Ndogs, cows, horses,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,bunnies, and even\Nlittle birdies, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,My dream is to gather up\Nas many animals as I can find
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,and open Hayama Park,\Nmy island sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:08.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat an amazing idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost like\Nshe has a heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Well, at least\NI have a brain, piggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you\Nliked animals so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have any pets at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Yeah. We have a sweet\Nlittle kitty cat named Bel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,He's the most adorable\Nthing in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Bel is short for\NMister Beelzebub.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\N"Beelzebub! A prince of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Also known as Lord of the Flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A demon who takes\Nthe form of a fly!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,That's her pet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The poor little baby was\Njust swarming with flies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:39.07,Main,,0,0,0,,when we took him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,That's where he got his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[TEACHER 2A] Hayama,\Ncan I borrow you a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.20,Main,,0,0,0,,If you make sure\Nthat everyone gets
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,one of these before\Nnext class, that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[TEACHER 2A] Can you also\Ncollect homework during break?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone should have\Na notebook to turn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NMan, that's a lot of worksheets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I must have been crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama is such a good student.\NObviously she's no demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:03.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems like it\Nmust be awfully difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.39,Main,,0,0,0,,to be the class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I didn't\Nwant to take the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The teachers insisted,\Nthough, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But if you didn't want to,\Ncouldn't you have refused?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm... Well, even though\NI kinda hate doing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.07,Main,,0,0,0,,all the extra work all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gonna look amazing\Non my resume, so here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NHuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2F]\NI studied really hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2L]\NThere's always next time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You're tenth in our grade.\NGreat job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:36.25,Main,,0,0,0,,So what's Hayama's rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NAh! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say it!\NI don't wanna hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NIt's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Grades aren't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,There's much more\Nto you than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Look on the bright side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You're ranked a lot higher\Nthan you were in middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What really matters\Nis you're improving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I am so sick and tired of\Nthat smug little teacher's pet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,always getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be class rep, but\Nof course they gave it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanted it so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] I mean, why did\Nthey choose her, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Just because she looks the part?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:07.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's not because\Nshe's smart and responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:14.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA whining]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this girl\Na friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, Hayama had a\Nlittle chat with her once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It was kinda brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.17,Main,,0,0,0,,She said being\Nclass representative
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,was going to my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It hurt my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:24.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:26.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2G]\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2I]\NWhat's wrong with Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2H]\NPoor thing's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2M]\NIs she getting bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NYou won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] Wow, people say\Nthat in real life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! I need a moment.\NThat was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl's got skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she is\Na demon, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[TEACHER 2B] All right, now that\Nwe've gone over the equation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,let's test your ability\Nto apply it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Todoroki, come to the board\Nand try the first problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[TODOROKI]\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:50.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[P.E. TEACHER 2A]\NPush it! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Get those legs moving, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I hate these timed runs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't we just have\Na snack instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Look at Hayama!\NShe's doing really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Wait, no she's not.\NI'm gonna lap her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[P.E. TEACHER 2A]\NC'mon, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Run like you mean it, or I'll\Nhave you doing laps all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NDon't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't talk\Nback to a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Just keep it all inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:20.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA pants]\NI'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NHey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHow could I be? She's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.83,Main,,0,0,0,,She was trying to\Nrun us to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NHow the mighty have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Even the great Hayama\Nhas a weakness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NNishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Quit being a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NIt's okay. Don't mind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.63,Main,,0,0,0,,The poor little thing\Nonly looks down on people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.21,Main,,0,0,0,,to make herself feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.30,Main,,0,0,0,,She deserves our pity\Nmore than our anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:49.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't need anybody's pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course you don't!\NYou're not little!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got a great figure.\NIt's nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] Why are we\Ntalking about my figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I do think it's important to\Ntake care of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,A balanced diet and proper\Nexercise can do wonders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NBooyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:06.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NThat must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to watch what you\Neat and work out all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.91,Main,,0,0,0,,to maintain your weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought that only\Nhappened to old people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NThat's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:13.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not what I was saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you always\Ntwist my words?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat? I don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,She does have skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:24.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2K]\NBye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:25.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 2J]\NSee you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I still feel\Nlike I'm gonna vomit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] You really don't\Nlike running, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I just don't have the stamina\Nto go on and on like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I don't think I\Ncould run another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.65,Main,,0,0,0,,So much for not\Nrunning another step!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[KITTENS meow]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Were they abandoned?\NWhaddaya think we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:53.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at how tiny\Nand helpless they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.71,Main,,0,0,0,,How could anybody\Nabandon them like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NShe may hide it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,but Hayama actually has\Na kind and gentle spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\N"Please take care of us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take care of whoever\Nabandoned these poor kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of them so well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,they'll wish they\Nhad never been born!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:17.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO, FUTABA]\NYup, she's a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I was able to find\Nhomes for two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.81,Main,,0,0,0,,That leaves one more, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it won't be easy,\Nbut maybe I can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'll have to move somewhere\Nthat allows pets first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Slow down, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh. I can't be the only person\Nat this school who loves cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NDid you say cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] I don't know\Nif it helps, but Nishiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,used to have a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NA cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you care,\Nbut yes I had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It passed away\Nabout three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NYour family had that cat since
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,before you were born, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You must've really loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna talk\Nabout it anymore, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NOh, Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I never, ever thought\NI would say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.77,Main,,0,0,0,,but you're actually\Ngood for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.52,Main,,0,0,0,,If you were aiming for\Na compliment, you missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:10.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWelcome to your new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\NI agreed to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] Well, it's not\Nlike I had much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.88,Main,,0,0,0,,And this has nothing\Nto do with Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's only for the kitten's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[KITTEN meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[KITTEN meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:45.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[KITTEN meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to find a\Nname for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] You're gonna be\Naround a long time, I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.63,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, girls.\NLet's get down to business!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! We have to\Ncome up with nicknames
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.85,Main,,0,0,0,,for each other, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,It slipped my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's something we need to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't be real friends until\Nwe have nicknames, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly sure\Nthat's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I humbly ask this favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.65,Main,,0,0,0,,As a sign of our friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.53,Main,,0,0,0,,will you please\Ngive me a nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA]\NWell, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Loco Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Purple Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NNot approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhat, you don't like either one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:48.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NUgh! No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,They are entirely unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You should be striving for\Nsomething noble, intellectual,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:56.42,Main,,0,0,0,,something that connotes beauty,\Ngrace, and magnanimity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,--Former Rich Chick!\N--Purple Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO growls]\NDid you even hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] Please address\NMiss Yoko as "Miss Yoko."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Hey, look who's popping\Nout of the bushes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:10.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] You appeared so\Nsuddenly without making a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you were\Na stalker or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NA stalker? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.86,Main,,0,0,0,,But anyway, the only name\Nthat truly fits Miss Yoko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:16.99,Main,,0,0,0,,is "Miss Yoko."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:17.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Like your new nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I had thought my nickname\Nwould be something different,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,not the name I've\Nalways been called by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,So, that's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko is officially\NMiss Yoko now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You're next, Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:37.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't actually\Nknow your first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] I mean, mine's\NFutaba, hers is Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,But yours is some big\Nmystery for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NIsn't this nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, there's nothing\Nlike a picnic on a sunny day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:53.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NAw, c'mon. It's only fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You know our first names;\Nyou should tell us yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, stop stonewalling\Nand tell us already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what are you\Ndoing after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm not really sure--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why\Nyou're making such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--Just tell us your first name!\N--[KOU] Hey, Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:15.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That's your name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO, FUTABA gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,There, you know.\NAre you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru. Terry? Ter-Bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, relax.\NIt's really cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.\NI think it's quite lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.11,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll come up with a\Ngreat nickname for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:38.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NLeave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot to pack chopsticks\Nwith my lunch this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.82,Main,,0,0,0,,and I don't know\Nwhat to do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I'm sure they\Nhave disposable ones
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,in the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew you were\Nthe person to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.\NI'd be totally lost without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We haven't met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of Hayama's?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually I'm more\Nthan just a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Teru's older sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Her sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Is it truly possible\Nthey're related?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.64,Main,,0,0,0,,A demon and an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You know April Fool's Day\Nhas come and gone, don't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Just drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway,\Nit's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I'm\NTeru's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:20.32,Main,,0,0,0,,My name's Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, hello!\NIt's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Hold on a second,\Nare you Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:25.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NHa, I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait here and\NI'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:34.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Here, take one.\NI made them from scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:38.92,Main,,0,0,0,,--That's so nice, thank you.\N--[FUTABA] Ooh! Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NWould you like to try one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Down the hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] This candy really packs\Na punch of nutrients!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:55.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It's made from fermented beans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:55.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Please take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,A girl can't live on bread\Ncrusts alone, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I know my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:04.07,Main,,0,0,0,,She seems sweet, but she's\Nnot always the nicest person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll stay friends\Nwith her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Never mind what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.74,Main,,0,0,0,,She has a pretty bad habit\Nof running her mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.62,Main,,0,0,0,,before her brain gets involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Kind of a ditz, but harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:15.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What's a ditz?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry up, you won't\Nget to eat any lunch at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NWell, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,The candies were good,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:24.67,Main,,0,0,0,,but I think they can\Nbe better, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll try a different\Nrecipe next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[BEELZEBUB meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:46.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Come on, Bel,\Nit's still really early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I should get to sleep\Nin a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what weekends are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:52.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[BEELZEBUB meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA cooing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA gasps]\NWhere'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Time to get up, sleepy head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:06.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're chipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Are you excited\Nabout breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make a\Nsmoothie for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.64,Main,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] This morning's\Nsecret ingredients
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,are garlic and banana!\N[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I'm gonna\Nsleep a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NAww.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Well in that case,\NI'll see if Bel wants to try
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,some of my\Nsuper-special smoothie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,So gross. More than gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:32.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just plain wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NHey, Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going shopping today.\NDo ya wanna come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NThis is nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile since\Nwe've gone out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NSure has.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what all do we need to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NJust a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I need some books.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I would try\Nto find a good cookbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.47,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'd love a photo album!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:56.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NHayama! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, look! It's Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you girls just out\Nhaving a sister-bonding day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep. We haven't spent nearly\Nenough time together lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.82,Main,,0,0,0,,so I dragged her out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I always wanted a sister,\Nbut I'm an only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] At least no one's\Ntrying to poison you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You getting your weekend\Nshopping done, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna pick up\Nsome giblets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh! That gives me an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,The grocery store's\Nright over there, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:31.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Hey, hold on.\NIs that really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NHere, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll have giblets, Chinese yam,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,okra, and mulukhiyah\Nall mixed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.68,Main,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be\Nmy best candy yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NBlegh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Why the obsession with\Nmaking health foods into candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that kinda\Ndefeat the purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the only way\Nsome people would try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS shouting]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANNOUNCER 2A] Today only,\Nwe're having a special sale
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.70,Main,,0,0,0,,on mayonnaise!\NThat's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.57,Main,,0,0,0,,We're knocking 50%\Noff the regular price!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:54.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Cheap mayonnaise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANNOUNCER 2A]\NYou don't want to miss out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry, while supplies last!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:02.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NAgainst all odds, I succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:06.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I've acquired my very own\Nbottle of discount mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:09.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA]\NHow embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Out of every store in the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I ended up\Nrunning into you ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you\Nwant to give me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.68,Main,,0,0,0,,all of these raffle\Ntickets, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't worry\Nabout it, we have plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you seen the prizes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Fifth place gets tissues,\Nfourth, a coffee set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's really not that exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Third place is a bag of rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Not you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:37.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoop-di-doo,\Na bunch of tissues.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I love my brand\Nnew coffee set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Check it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThat's a huge bag of rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Ack! The only thing\NI really wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.34,Main,,0,0,0,,and the "demon"\Ngets to take it home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[bell ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[RAFFLE MAN 2A] Congratulations\Nto our big winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Can someone give me\Na hand with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:01.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO, FUTABA]\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NThis happens a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,She has pretty good luck\Nwith this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd call that more\Nthan pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.98,Main,,0,0,0,,She's also the one who got\Nus those bathhouse tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NOh, that was her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:12.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Please! I can't\Ncarry it all myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NI'm exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It was really nice of Yoko and\NFutaba to take the heavy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give the hot springs\Nvacation to Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot to\Ngo to the bookstore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:30.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Why even bother\Nbuying a cookbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like you're gonna\Nfollow the recipes, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Yeah, but I wish\NI'd got a photo album.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhy do you need that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:40.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I was looking\Nthrough the closet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:42.93,Main,,0,0,0,,and I found a bunch\Nof old pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,They brought back\Nso many memories
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,from when we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NBe careful up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Please don't fall, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You know I'm a\Nreal good climber!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NA little further. Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:11.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I've just gotta\Ncatch this butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:14.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru's gonna love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That was kinda dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NI don't know if you remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.69,Main,,0,0,0,,but when we were younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,you used to get sick\Nand hurt really easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty healthy now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.08,Main,,0,0,0,,But you should still\Ntake care of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:50.17,Main,,0,0,0,,and make sure you're getting\Nlots of vitamins and minerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NIs that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that why she's always going\Non and on about nutrients?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NIt's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll try to make something\Nnutritious, and tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:07.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NBecause she's worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:11.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NKou made these as thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.46,Main,,0,0,0,,for helping us out yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NHomemade rice balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Stuffed with liver, white roe,\Nand bitter melon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:36.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,But what about all the\Nstuff you bought yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:40.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm all about staying healthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,but this is taking things\Na little too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I'm sure Hayama's\Nsister put in a lot of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,and effort into\Nmaking these for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.97,Main,,0,0,0,,We owe it to her\Nto at least eat one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NOh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NShe's choking it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:56.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Thanks for taking\None for the team, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,How could you allow\NMiss Yoko to ingest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:22:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,such a vile thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:03.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... You really\Ndon't have to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Although I gotta admit, your\Ndedication is very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Stop that!\NDon't encourage her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:10.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Well, maybe they're\Nright when they say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:13.21,Main,,0,0,0,,nothing good for you is tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:14.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThis must be great for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NDon't encourage her, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NMiss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Being rich is\Nnot all that wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,But that does not mean\Nmy current life is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] You wouldn't\Nbe green after eating
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.14,Main,,0,0,0,,a strange rice ball, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.23,0:23:57.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO, FUTABA] But, all of us\Nbeing able to eat the rice balls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:23:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,that Hayama's sister\Nmade for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:00.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\N...makes us happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.65,0:24:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Your real\Nthoughts are leaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NMiss Yoko!
